Introduction

Liang Jiao (Chinese: 梁娇, Korean: 량자오) is a Chinese idol singer and a member of GNZ48's Team G.

In 2021, she was a contestant on the Korean survival show "Girls Planet 999". She was eliminated in the 8th episode after placing 9th in C-Group.

On December 29, 2022, Liang Jiao was revealed as a member of the new GNZ48 sub-unit, Nebulove.
